narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: This class pushed me to improve as both a photographer and artist (if there is a difference). I really appreciated the discourse relating to photography and working in photography. Overall, a fantastic experience. I would highly recommend anyone to take advanced photo if they are interested in growing as a photographer!

comments: I would highly recommend this course. The feedback from both Lisa and the other students in the class greatly improved my photographic practice.
